text: Icimauna pallidipennis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Martins and Galileo in 2007. It is known from Costa Rica.BioLib.cz - Icimauna pallidipennis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 2007
